channel.title: Comments on: Meeting of the mind: Robert Plant and Jessica Simpson

item.title: By: ryno
item.dc:creator: ryno
item.description: Two blondes walk into a bar; one is a dingy media sensation and the other is one of the biggest music icons of all time... "Look at this." says one to the other. You can now use your imagination to decide who said what. It'll be great to see what everyone else thinks!

item.title: By: Diana
item.dc:creator: Diana
item.description:
That was cruel to say about Jessica. When you say hurtful things.. there are people out there with feelings. Think before you swing axes.
Robert Plant is most likely a very wonderful and kind person. He's probably looking at her and thinking how beautiful she is. Atleast that's what I'd like to think. Be kind. Life is short.
